    public static class AccessibilityEventScrollStepStrategy.NullAccessibilityEventScrollStepStrategy
extends AccessibilityEventScrollStepStrategy
    Some widgets may not always fire correct AccessibilityEvent. Detecting end by null event is safer (at the cost of a extra scroll) than examining indices.
